message.body: I can't fall asleep baby!
Good morning baby! Just texting to tell you that I love you!
Good morning, beauty :) I love you too!! Nd i hope youre ready for a nice day :)
Not necessarily a nice day because I have a chem lab, but hopefully it'll be okay!
It'll be perfectly ok! No worries, my love. And...todays shorter than yesterday haha. Thats already a win.
Haha. A win. It'll be a win for you since you can sleep!
...took 2 hr nap last night...didnt wake up until 5am. Im feeling uh...like a million bucks. But uh...oops haha.
Today will for once be productive. Applications and ive got lots of hw.
Okay! Good good.
Didn't you have work last night?
Hahaha. You're crazy!
Haha im sure i'll hear all about it on friday. But i was dying. And i have shit to do that i will now be awake to do. Oops. But this is much better.
Did you call?
I wasnt planning on skipping at all. By time i woke up...not too long ago haha...pretty sure they figured out i wasnt coming by now
Haha. Oh man. Well...I prefer when you sleep :)
I agree :) Feeling much better
Good!
I'm tired baby. So tired. I don't wanna be here anymore.
Oh my love, i understand completely. Not too much longer and you can pack up and head back towards home and relaxing.
Oyyy. I do not feel like doing anything. Haha. I don't even wanna go to micro. Part of me is sincerely thinking about not going. For serials.
Haha what can we do to motivate you to power through?
Nothing!!! Send me home!
Ahah ok! You go home now!
Haha. Okay! Yay!
But in all seriousness, I really don't want to do anything today. I wanna go home. No lab. No class!
Hah dang my love. You rebel. Do what ever you need to do, darling.
I have to go to lab, and I feel obligated to go to micro.
I just don't want tooooo! But I am skipping on the 13th so I don't wanna do that.
Hm i see. Guilt is a nasty bugger. You sure you cant push through? Do you have a little break?
I've been in the library since 8:45. My class is at 12:30 and then I'll have a break from 1:20-2:30.
I actually wish I could just get everything done an over with.
Yeah, seriously. You think getting to school so early is messing with you. Stinks sittng in library all day long. Maybe stay home on fridays til class?
It probably is. But I do it so that I can get a ride from gabby. Besides, I always have homework to do. I'm sure when I'm in lab and class it'll be okay.
Agreed. You'll be good. And hope it is productive. Just a looong time to sit. Mix it up! Take a break. Take a stroll. Breath freee!
Hahaha. It's probably also from lack of sleep. I fell asleep at like 1:30 and woke up at 6 :( Boo.
Oof. Sorry, love. You gotsta get some sleep then. Dont go crazy with chem tonight. But, is it ok if i hop in the shower? Gotta start my day haha
Yes. Hehe. I guess I can let you go.
Haha dont wanna go. I want us in the same place. Foreva haha.
ï¿¼Is you gonna help me eat this? Is too big fo me.
YESSSS. I HAVENT EATEN ANYTHING SINCE THIS MORNING!
WHAT!? WHY?! Stop doing that crazy! And come get your jumbo slice of salvadorian supreme chorizo pizza!!
It looks so delicious. I'm eating now :)
Phew. Thank you for diving right into dinner! And i was quite pleased haha. Only the freshest ingredients from the neighborhood los primos ha. Still half for u
I want it!!! Haha
Haha come here!!! I'll make it for you again haha. Now time to just be stuffed and watch tv :) Would very much like it if you were here. Very very much :)
